  <mainDescription>This task sets in place control techniques for monitoring the plan's performance. Usually this entails a systematic review&#xD;
of all aspects of the plan against targets set, usually on a monthly or quarterly basis. The review must be carried out&#xD;
regularly to ensure prompt attention and action in areas when the results lag behind targets set. Managers and others&#xD;
responsible for implementation of all elements of the action programme should be involved in the monitoring process</mainDescription>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
